== On your Mac: 

1. Install Xcode and Command Line Tools ( $ xcode-select --install ) 
2. Install RVM https://rvm.io/rvm/install/ 
3. Install homebrew http://brew.sh/ 
4. $ brew install chromedriver 
5. $ git clone git@github.com:richdownie/safari_selenium.git
6. $ cd safari_selenium 
7. $ rvm install ruby-2.1.5 
8. $ gem install bundler 